Feature: Unwind clause

  Background:
    Given a graph with space named "nba"

  Scenario: unwind return
    When executing query:
      """
      UNWIND [1, 2, 3] AS a
      RETURN a
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | a |
      | 1 |
      | 2 |
      | 3 |
    When executing query:
      """
      UNWIND [1, NULL, 3] AS a
      RETURN a
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | a    |
      | 1    |
      | NULL |
      | 3    |
